name: flower girl activity kits - set of three - discounted price
description:
weddings are a long day for everyone - but can feel even longer for the kids!!

here's a great activity kit to keep the little ones busy and you stressed free- at a discounted price of $9.

these kits are also great for a rainy day or long car trips! convo me for relabeling options or as aparty favor.

the "flower girl" activity kit includes:

goldfish crackers
stickers
a wedding activity placemat
crayons
bubbles
lollipops
a napkin
a moist towelette

ring bearer and kid's activity kits also available.
i can also add the child's name to the label.
custom color ribbon belts available to match your wedding colors.

please email me with any questions or custom orders.
